West Spruill has been charged with murdering Ann Charle, 36, on Monday evening in the Bronx . 
  The mother-of-two was walking towards her car when he allegedly pulled out a gun and ordered her into her Honda at gunpoint . 
  Police say he sexually assaulted her in her car but she escaped and ran naked down the street . 
  He allegedly chased after her and shot her in the head and chest . 
  Her body was found just a block away from Project Renewal shelter where she worked . 
  Spruil was charged with murder and criminal possession of a weapon . 
 